  "3052510": {
    "name": "Oceaneers",
    "steam_appid": 3052510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制一群被困的幸存者，努力在一个被洪水淹没的世界中保持漂浮。这里唯一的陆地是可能会沉没的不稳定岛屿！您需建立一个完美的岛屿殖民地，让您的幸存者快乐地生活，并保护他们免受陆地和海洋危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/ad99219cabcb081dc15d2050050b0cfa.webp?t=1771468580\" width=600 height=53 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在浮岛上生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上的生活并非只有阳光和椰子。在资源稀缺、岛屿空间有限的情况下，规划至关重要。您需要建造工作站，管理粮食生产，确保饮用水的供应，同时还要确保您的岛屿庇护所能保持漂浮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/58e8e95e8619643b66097f78e6cbb4db.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/58e8e95e8619643b66097f78e6cbb4db.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/58e8e95e8619643b66097f78e6cbb4db.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/86b8ece912721a97724594146e11c57d.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/86b8ece912721a97724594146e11c57d.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/86b8ece912721a97724594146e11c57d.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握木筏制作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计并建造您自己的木筏！从一个简单的划桨开始，然后研究大型木筏和更强大的引擎，将岛屿运送回您的主基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/03802fcaf912f5724b14d6cb73c76acc.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/03802fcaf912f5724b14d6cb73c76acc.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/03802fcaf912f5724b14d6cb73c76acc.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用浮力技术保持漂浮</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一家神秘的洪水前公司重新发现岛屿浮力技术。建造预警系统并研究装置，让您的岛屿保持漂浮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/3e2307d333448292d22b79d57b7a0381.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/3e2307d333448292d22b79d57b7a0381.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/3e2307d333448292d22b79d57b7a0381.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开展探险！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个小小的岛屿不足以实现长期生存……派遣幸存者进行探险，从不同的生物群落收集资源。在岛屿沉没或漂走之前，尽可能多地收集物资。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/22c05ad4aefc9f43fac843084ce553f0.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/22c05ad4aefc9f43fac843084ce553f0.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/22c05ad4aefc9f43fac843084ce553f0.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抵御来自天气、岛屿和海洋的威胁</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护您的殖民地免受恶劣天气和陆地及海洋的威胁。加固您的木筏，使您的建筑物防风雨，并制定反制措施，应对会偷食的海鸥、会夹脚的螃蟹和会破坏木筏的鲨鱼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/a6f6c7396a832d04478d630b68c0cf44.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/a6f6c7396a832d04478d630b68c0cf44.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/a6f6c7396a832d04478d630b68c0cf44.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 在单人游戏中控制多个角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 将更多的岛屿拖运到您的殖民地，扩展您的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 通过装置改善岛屿的浮力，使其保持漂浮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 研究并解锁高级工作站和升级选项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 在陆地和海洋上抵御天气事件和各种威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 种植作物、准备口粮并烹饪食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 管理幸存者的需求，并通过完成任务获得经验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/084fc57d72dd337fd79d74cbd4c1162e.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/f679ec07367ad6bd6bce42a002992e1a.poster.avif?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/f679ec07367ad6bd6bce42a002992e1a.webm?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/f679ec07367ad6bd6bce42a002992e1a.mp4?t=1771468580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052510/extras/de3b6e63c4be04a5103f55387c6ebab0.webp?t=1771468580\" width=780 height=20 /></span></p>",
